{
  "video_id": "iw7nPE2jioU",
  "title": "How we can help young people build a better future | Henrietta Fore",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13560.0,
      "end_time": 18256.0,
      "text": "Today, there are 1.8 billion young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18280.0,
      "end_time": 21920.0,
      "text": "between the ages of 10 and 24 in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22920.0,
      "end_time": 26656.0,
      "text": "It is the largest cohort in human history."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26680.0,
      "end_time": 29616.0,
      "text": "Meeting their needs will be a big challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29640.0,
      "end_time": 32776.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s also a big opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32800.0,
      "end_time": 37336.0,
      "text": "They hold our shared future in their hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37360.0,
      "end_time": 43176.0,
      "text": "Every day, we read about young people lending their ideas and passions"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 43200.0,
      "end_time": 45216.0,
      "text": "to fighting for change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45240.0,
      "end_time": 50496.0,
      "text": "social change, political change, change in their communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 50520.0,
      "end_time": 54640.0,
      "text": "Imagine what they&#39;ll create: breakthroughs, inventions."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55480.0,
      "end_time": 59696.0,
      "text": "Maybe new medicines, new modes of transportation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59720.0,
      "end_time": 61736.0,
      "text": "new ways to communicate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 61760.0,
      "end_time": 67295.0,
      "text": "sustainable economies and maybe even a world at peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 67320.0,
      "end_time": 70216.0,
      "text": "But this opportunity, this youth dividend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 70240.0,
      "end_time": 71679.0,
      "text": "is not a given."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 73200.0,
      "end_time": 77960.0,
      "text": "One point eight billion young women and young men"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 77120.0,
      "end_time": 79640.0,
      "text": "are standing at the door of adulthood."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 80520.0,
      "end_time": 82256.0,
      "text": "Are they ready?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 82280.0,
      "end_time": 84640.0,
      "text": "Right now, too few of them are."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 85520.0,
      "end_time": 88136.0,
      "text": "My favorite part of my job at UNICEF"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 92696.0,
      "text": "is a chance to talk to, meet with and hear from young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 92720.0,
      "end_time": 94656.0,
      "text": "all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94680.0,
      "end_time": 97576.0,
      "text": "And they tell me about their hopes and dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 97600.0,
      "end_time": 100655.0,
      "text": "And they have amazing hopes and dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 100680.0,
      "end_time": 103800.0,
      "text": "for what they&#39;ll accomplish in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103960.0,
      "end_time": 107600.0,
      "text": "But what they&#39;re also telling me is that they have fears."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 108400.0,
      "end_time": 113336.0,
      "text": "They feel that they&#39;re facing a series of urgent crises."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 113360.0,
      "end_time": 115936.0,
      "text": "A crisis of demographics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 115960.0,
      "end_time": 118336.0,
      "text": "a crisis of education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 118360.0,
      "end_time": 120616.0,
      "text": "a crisis of employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 120640.0,
      "end_time": 122696.0,
      "text": "a crisis of violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 122720.0,
      "end_time": 124960.0,
      "text": "and a crisis for girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 127240.0,
      "end_time": 131616.0,
      "text": "If you look at these crises, you realize that they&#39;re urgent"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131640.0,
      "end_time": 134550.0,
      "text": "and they need to be addressed now."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134800.0,
      "end_time": 136560.0,
      "text": "Because they tell us that they&#39;re worried."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137560.0,
      "end_time": 142256.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re worried that they might not get the education that they need."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 142280.0,
      "end_time": 143496.0,
      "text": "And you know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 143520.0,
      "end_time": 145960.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re right."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 145120.0,
      "end_time": 148936.0,
      "text": "Two hundred million adolescents are out of school worldwide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 148960.0,
      "end_time": 151616.0,
      "text": "about the population of Brazil."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 151640.0,
      "end_time": 153616.0,
      "text": "And those that are in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153640.0,
      "end_time": 157550.0,
      "text": "feel that they may not be getting the right skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 157800.0,
      "end_time": 161376.0,
      "text": "Globally, six in 10 children and young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 161400.0,
      "end_time": 166640.0,
      "text": "do not meet the minimum proficiency level for reading and mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 167360.0,
      "end_time": 169856.0,
      "text": "No country can be successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169880.0,
      "end_time": 173296.0,
      "text": "if nearly half of its population of young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 173320.0,
      "end_time": 175840.0,
      "text": "are unable to read or write."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 176680.0,
      "end_time": 180856.0,
      "text": "And what about the lucky few who are in secondary school?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180880.0,
      "end_time": 184550.0,
      "text": "Many of them are dropping out because they&#39;re worried"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 184800.0,
      "end_time": 188256.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re not getting skills that they can use to make a livelihood."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 188280.0,
      "end_time": 192216.0,
      "text": "And sometimes, their parents can no longer afford the fees."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 192240.0,
      "end_time": 193440.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tragedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 194480.0,
      "end_time": 199335.0,
      "text": "And young people are also telling me that they&#39;re worried about employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 199360.0,
      "end_time": 201440.0,
      "text": "that they won&#39;t be able to find a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 202120.0,
      "end_time": 203760.0,
      "text": "And again, they&#39;re right."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 204480.0,
      "end_time": 208880.0,
      "text": "Every month, 10 million young people reach working age."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 209760.0,
      "end_time": 211896.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a staggering number."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 211920.0,
      "end_time": 217136.0,
      "text": "Some will go on for further education, but many will enter the workforce."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 221480.0,
      "text": "And our world is not creating 10 million new jobs each month."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 222400.0,
      "end_time": 226120.0,
      "text": "The competition is fierce for the jobs that are available."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 227000.0,
      "end_time": 229896.0,
      "text": "So, imagine being a young person today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 229920.0,
      "end_time": 233136.0,
      "text": "needing a job, seeking a livelihood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 235216.0,
      "text": "ready to build a future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 235240.0,
      "end_time": 238000.0,
      "text": "and opportunities are hard to find."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 240120.0,
      "end_time": 242960.0,
      "text": "Young people are also telling me"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 242120.0,
      "end_time": 245856.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re worried that they&#39;re not getting the skills that they need."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 245880.0,
      "end_time": 247680.0,
      "text": "And again, they&#39;re right."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 249840.0,
      "end_time": 254216.0,
      "text": "We are finding ourselves at a time in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 254240.0,
      "end_time": 257216.0,
      "text": "when the world is changing so fast for work."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 257240.0,
      "end_time": 260616.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re in the fourth industrial revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 260640.0,
      "end_time": 264816.0,
      "text": "Young people do not want to be on the farms and in rural communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 264840.0,
      "end_time": 266856.0,
      "text": "They want to go to the cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 266880.0,
      "end_time": 270856.0,
      "text": "They want to learn future skills for future work."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 270880.0,
      "end_time": 275135.0,
      "text": "They want to learn digital technology and green technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 275160.0,
      "end_time": 278776.0,
      "text": "They want to have a chance to learn modern agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 278800.0,
      "end_time": 281536.0,
      "text": "They want to learn business and entrepreneurship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 281560.0,
      "end_time": 284616.0,
      "text": "so that they can create a business of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 284640.0,
      "end_time": 290176.0,
      "text": "They want to be nurses and radiologists and pharmacists and doctors."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 290200.0,
      "end_time": 294800.0,
      "text": "And they want to have all of the skills that they&#39;ll need for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 294960.0,
      "end_time": 300455.0,
      "text": "They also want to learn the trades, like construction and electricians."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 300480.0,
      "end_time": 303456.0,
      "text": "These are all the professions that a country needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 303480.0,
      "end_time": 306760.0,
      "text": "as well as the professions that have not been invented yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 308800.0,
      "end_time": 312760.0,
      "text": "And young people are also telling me that they&#39;re worried about violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 313720.0,
      "end_time": 318656.0,
      "text": "At home, online, in school, in their communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 318680.0,
      "end_time": 320760.0,
      "text": "And again, they&#39;re right."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 321560.0,
      "end_time": 325856.0,
      "text": "A young person can have hundreds of friends on social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 325880.0,
      "end_time": 328856.0,
      "text": "but when they need to find a friendly face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 328880.0,
      "end_time": 331936.0,
      "text": "someone who can be there as their friend, to talk to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 331960.0,
      "end_time": 334176.0,
      "text": "they do not find one."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 334200.0,
      "end_time": 338216.0,
      "text": "They face bullying, harassment and more."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 338240.0,
      "end_time": 342256.0,
      "text": "And hundreds of millions are facing exploitation"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 342280.0,
      "end_time": 344320.0,
      "text": "and abuse, and violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 345360.0,
      "end_time": 349376.0,
      "text": "Every seven minutes, an adolescent boy or girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 349400.0,
      "end_time": 353120.0,
      "text": "somewhere in the world is killed by an act of violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 355400.0,
      "end_time": 356775.0,
      "text": "And girls are telling me"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 356800.0,
      "end_time": 360960.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re especially worried about their futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 360120.0,
      "end_time": 362776.0,
      "text": "And sadly, they&#39;re right, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 362800.0,
      "end_time": 365856.0,
      "text": "Girls face prejudice and discrimination."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 365880.0,
      "end_time": 367896.0,
      "text": "They face early childhood marriage"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 367920.0,
      "end_time": 371320.0,
      "text": "and they face life-threatening early pregnancy."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 372760.0,
      "end_time": 375575.0,
      "text": "Imagine a population of the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 375600.0,
      "end_time": 377560.0,
      "text": "Now double it."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 377800.0,
      "end_time": 381856.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the number of women who were married before their 18th birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 381880.0,
      "end_time": 384616.0,
      "text": "Six hundred and fifty million."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 384640.0,
      "end_time": 389000.0,
      "text": "And many were mothers while they were still children themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 390000.0,
      "end_time": 394536.0,
      "text": "One out of every three women will face physical abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 394560.0,
      "end_time": 397800.0,
      "text": "or sexual abuse in her lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 397920.0,
      "end_time": 401320.0,
      "text": "So, no wonder girls are worried about their futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 402400.0,
      "end_time": 407936.0,
      "text": "These urgent crises may not be a reality in your life or in your neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 407960.0,
      "end_time": 410895.0,
      "text": "And perhaps you&#39;ve had opportunities for a good education"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 410920.0,
      "end_time": 414536.0,
      "text": "and for marketable skills, and for getting a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 414560.0,
      "end_time": 419656.0,
      "text": "And maybe you&#39;ve never faced violence, or prejudice, or discrimination."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 419680.0,
      "end_time": 424160.0,
      "text": "But there are tens of millions of young people who are not so lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 424400.0,
      "end_time": 428496.0,
      "text": "And they are sounding the alarm for their futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 428520.0,
      "end_time": 432575.0,
      "text": "And that is why UNICEF and our many public and private partners"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 432600.0,
      "end_time": 435576.0,
      "text": "are launching a new global initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 435600.0,
      "end_time": 438616.0,
      "text": "Young people themselves have named it."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 438640.0,
      "end_time": 441575.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s called Generation Unlimited"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 441600.0,
      "end_time": 445320.0,
      "text": "or Gen-U or Gen you."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 446720.0,
      "end_time": 451456.0,
      "text": "So, what they&#39;re saying is, it&#39;s our time, it&#39;s our turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 451480.0,
      "end_time": 452920.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 453760.0,
      "end_time": 456695.0,
      "text": "Our goal is very straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 456720.0,
      "end_time": 461576.0,
      "text": "We want every young person in school, learning, training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 461600.0,
      "end_time": 465320.0,
      "text": "or age-appropriate employment by the year 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 466880.0,
      "end_time": 471256.0,
      "text": "This goal is urgent, it&#39;s necessary, it&#39;s ambitious."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 471280.0,
      "end_time": 473559.0,
      "text": "But we think it&#39;s also achievable."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 474480.0,
      "end_time": 477216.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re calling out for cutting-edge solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 477240.0,
      "end_time": 479960.0,
      "text": "and new ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 479120.0,
      "end_time": 484560.0,
      "text": "Ideas that will give young people a fighting chance for their futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 484800.0,
      "end_time": 485816.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know all the answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 485840.0,
      "end_time": 490215.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;re reaching out to businesses and governments, and nonprofits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 490240.0,
      "end_time": 494856.0,
      "text": "and academia, and communities, and innovators for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 494880.0,
      "end_time": 497695.0,
      "text": "Gen-U is to be an open platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 497720.0,
      "end_time": 502776.0,
      "text": "where people can come and share their ideas and solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 502800.0,
      "end_time": 505936.0,
      "text": "about what works, what does not work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 505960.0,
      "end_time": 509159.0,
      "text": "and importantly, what might work."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 510400.0,
      "end_time": 515560.0,
      "text": "So if we can take these ideas and add a little bit of seed money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 515799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517559.99999999994,
      "text": "and add some good partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 517799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519335.99999999994,
      "text": "and add good political will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 519360.0,
      "end_time": 523576.0,
      "text": "we think they can scale up to reach thousands and millions of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 523600.0,
      "end_time": 524799.0,
      "text": "around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 525720.0,
      "end_time": 529216.0,
      "text": "And with this project, we&#39;re also going to do something new."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 529240.0,
      "end_time": 532856.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to co-design and co-create with young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 532880.0,
      "end_time": 535775.0,
      "text": "So with Gen-U, they&#39;re going to be in the driver&#39;s seat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 535799.0,
      "end_time": 537800.0,
      "text": "steering us all along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 539280.0,
      "end_time": 543415.0,
      "text": "In Argentina, there&#39;s a program where we connect students"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 543440.0,
      "end_time": 548496.0,
      "text": "who are in rural, remote, hard to reach mountainous communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 548520.0,
      "end_time": 551136.0,
      "text": "with something they&#39;ve seldom seen:"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 551160.0,
      "end_time": 553656.0,
      "text": "a secondary school teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 553680.0,
      "end_time": 559295.0,
      "text": "So these students come to a classroom, they&#39;re joined by a community teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 559320.0,
      "end_time": 563536.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re connected to urban schools online."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 563560.0,
      "end_time": 566376.0,
      "text": "And there is the secondary school teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 566400.0,
      "end_time": 569776.0,
      "text": "who is teaching them about digital technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 569800.0,
      "end_time": 572656.0,
      "text": "and a good secondary school education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 572680.0,
      "end_time": 576400.0,
      "text": "without them ever having to leave their own communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 577000.0,
      "end_time": 581176.0,
      "text": "And in South Africa, there&#39;s a program called Techno Girls."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 581200.0,
      "end_time": 583896.0,
      "text": "And these are girls from disadvantaged neighborhoods"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 583920.0,
      "end_time": 587216.0,
      "text": "who are studying the STEM program area:"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 587240.0,
      "end_time": 590376.0,
      "text": "science, technology, engineering and math."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 590400.0,
      "end_time": 593376.0,
      "text": "And they have a chance to job shadow."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 593400.0,
      "end_time": 595976.0,
      "text": "This is the way that they then can see themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 596000.0,
      "end_time": 598160.0,
      "text": "in jobs that are in engineering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 598400.0,
      "end_time": 601520.0,
      "text": "in science, and maybe in the space program."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 602320.0,
      "end_time": 603656.0,
      "text": "In Bangladesh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 603680.0,
      "end_time": 607695.0,
      "text": "we have partners who are training tens of thousands of young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 607720.0,
      "end_time": 609160.0,
      "text": "in the trades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 609400.0,
      "end_time": 612256.0,
      "text": "so that they can become motorcycle repair people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 612280.0,
      "end_time": 614736.0,
      "text": "or mobile phone service people."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 614760.0,
      "end_time": 618960.0,
      "text": "But these are a chance to see their own livelihoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 618120.0,
      "end_time": 621320.0,
      "text": "And maybe even to have a business of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 622400.0,
      "end_time": 624160.0,
      "text": "And in Vietnam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 624400.0,
      "end_time": 627856.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a program where we are pairing young entrepreneurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 627880.0,
      "end_time": 630896.0,
      "text": "with the needs in their own local communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 630920.0,
      "end_time": 633856.0,
      "text": "So with this program, a group gathered"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 633880.0,
      "end_time": 637776.0,
      "text": "and they decided that they would solve the problem of transportation"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 637800.0,
      "end_time": 641960.0,
      "text": "for people with disabilities in their communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 641120.0,
      "end_time": 643416.0,
      "text": "So with a mentor and a bit of seed funding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 643440.0,
      "end_time": 647400.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve now developed a new app to help the whole community."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 648280.0,
      "end_time": 652415.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve seen how these programs can make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 652440.0,
      "end_time": 656936.0,
      "text": "When I was in Lebanon, I visited a program called Girls Got IT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 656960.0,
      "end_time": 658760.0,
      "text": "or Girls Got It."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 659520.0,
      "end_time": 662576.0,
      "text": "And in this program, girls who have been studying"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 662600.0,
      "end_time": 665416.0,
      "text": "computer skills and the STEM program"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 665440.0,
      "end_time": 669696.0,
      "text": "have a chance to work side by side with young professionals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 669720.0,
      "end_time": 672576.0,
      "text": "so that they can learn firsthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 672600.0,
      "end_time": 677256.0,
      "text": "what it&#39;s like to be an architect, a designer or a scientist."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 677280.0,
      "end_time": 680496.0,
      "text": "And when you see these girls, smiles on their faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 680520.0,
      "end_time": 683216.0,
      "text": "the hot lights in their eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 683240.0,
      "end_time": 686816.0,
      "text": "they are so excited, they have hope for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 686840.0,
      "end_time": 689560.0,
      "text": "They want to change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 689800.0,
      "end_time": 692376.0,
      "text": "And now, with this program and these mentors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 692400.0,
      "end_time": 694240.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ll be able to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 695400.0,
      "end_time": 698976.0,
      "text": "But these ideas and programs are just a start."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 699000.0,
      "end_time": 702840.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll only reach a fraction of the young people that we need to reach."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 703640.0,
      "end_time": 707776.0,
      "text": "We want to take these ideas and find ways to scale them up."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 707800.0,
      "end_time": 710256.0,
      "text": "To reach more young people in more communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 710280.0,
      "end_time": 712976.0,
      "text": "in more places around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 713000.0,
      "end_time": 715320.0,
      "text": "And we want to dream big."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 716800.0,
      "end_time": 719776.0,
      "text": "Could every school, everywhere in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 719800.0,
      "end_time": 722616.0,
      "text": "no matter how remote or mountainous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 722640.0,
      "end_time": 724616.0,
      "text": "or even if it&#39;s in a refugee camp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 724640.0,
      "end_time": 728960.0,
      "text": "could they be connected to the internet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 728120.0,
      "end_time": 731976.0,
      "text": "Could we have instant translation for young people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 732000.0,
      "end_time": 734136.0,
      "text": "so that you could get a good education"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 734160.0,
      "end_time": 736760.0,
      "text": "in your own language, anywhere in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 737640.0,
      "end_time": 739960.0,
      "text": "And would it be possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 739120.0,
      "end_time": 743160.0,
      "text": "that we could connect the education in your school"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 743400.0,
      "end_time": 747496.0,
      "text": "with skills that you&#39;re going to need to get a job in your own community?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 747520.0,
      "end_time": 750720.0,
      "text": "So that you actually can move from school to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 752360.0,
      "end_time": 753616.0,
      "text": "And more."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 753640.0,
      "end_time": 755199.0,
      "text": "Can each one of us help?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 756000.0,
      "end_time": 759336.0,
      "text": "In our everyday lives and in our workplaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 759360.0,
      "end_time": 761800.0,
      "text": "are there ways that we could support young people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 762560.0,
      "end_time": 765616.0,
      "text": "Young people are asking us for apprenticeships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 765640.0,
      "end_time": 768696.0,
      "text": "for job shadowing, for internships."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 768720.0,
      "end_time": 769920.0,
      "text": "Could we do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 770840.0,
      "end_time": 774816.0,
      "text": "Young people are also asking us for work-study programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 774840.0,
      "end_time": 777816.0,
      "text": "places where they can learn and earn."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 777840.0,
      "end_time": 782456.0,
      "text": "Could we do this and could we reach out to a community that&#39;s nearby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 782480.0,
      "end_time": 785800.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s less advantaged, and help them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 786440.0,
      "end_time": 789856.0,
      "text": "Young people are also saying that they want to help other young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 789880.0,
      "end_time": 792856.0,
      "text": "They want more space and more voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 792880.0,
      "end_time": 795896.0,
      "text": "so that they can gather to help each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 795920.0,
      "end_time": 800160.0,
      "text": "In HIV centers, in refugee camps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 800400.0,
      "end_time": 804520.0,
      "text": "but also to stop online bullying and early child marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 805320.0,
      "end_time": 808976.0,
      "text": "We need ideas, we need ideas that are big and small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 809000.0,
      "end_time": 811520.0,
      "text": "ideas that are local and global."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 813240.0,
      "end_time": 816816.0,
      "text": "This, in the end, is our responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 816840.0,
      "end_time": 822736.0,
      "text": "A massive generation of young people are about to inherit our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 822760.0,
      "end_time": 827856.0,
      "text": "It is our duty to leave a legacy of hope and opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 827880.0,
      "end_time": 831296.0,
      "text": "for them but also with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 831320.0,
      "end_time": 834696.0,
      "text": "Young people are 25 percent of our population."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 834720.0,
      "end_time": 838656.0,
      "text": "But they are 100 percent of our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 838680.0,
      "end_time": 841776.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re calling out for a fighting chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 841800.0,
      "end_time": 844376.0,
      "text": "to build a better world."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 844400.0,
      "end_time": 847616.0,
      "text": "So their call should be our calling."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 847640.0,
      "end_time": 850496.0,
      "text": "The calling of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 850520.0,
      "end_time": 853856.0,
      "text": "The time is now, the need is urgent."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 853880.0,
      "end_time": 858320.0,
      "text": "And 1.8 billion young people are waiting."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 859440.0,
      "end_time": 860656.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 860680.0,
      "end_time": 864680.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}